analysis.description:
ProfitChain.invest (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#218-277) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- thisRound.totalInvestors == thisGroup.roundSize
group in ProfitChain.newGroup (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#148) is a local variable never initialiazed

ProfitChain.invest (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#218-277) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(thisGroup.active || thisRound.totalInvestors > 0) (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#226-227)
	- thisRound.totalInvestors == thisGroup.roundSize (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#261-266)
	- require(bool)(! isInvestorInRound(thisRound,investor)) (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#234)

ProfitChain.withdraw (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#280-289) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(balances[withdrawer] >= sum) (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#286)

ProfitChain.payAllInvitors (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#395-437) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- invitor == owner || _amount == 0 || _depth >= thisGroup.invitationFeeDepth || _relevantTime > thisGroup.members[_payer].joinTime.add(thisGroup.invitationFeePeriod.mul(86400)) (/unique_chucks/25/0xc5936b4e458c60f887a4f17d05d2f8162976e012.sol#400-414)
